        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Burbank property values are driven primarily by land size, useable land character, the position of the holding relative to Bulimba Creek and the surrounding bushland reserves, and the quality and configuration of equestrian or hobby-farm infrastructure on the block.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Burbank?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented Burbank acreage properties typically sell within 40 to 70 days. The buyer pool is smaller and more specific than a standard residential suburb, and a campaign needs the time to reach lifestyle buyers from across south-east Queensland.</p>
