        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Burbank's tightly held acreage character and proximity to Carindale and the eastern suburbs has supported steady demand from lifestyle buyers. Useable acreage inside the Brisbane City Council boundary is a scarce asset and continues to attract committed buyers.</p>
